title: The Amazing Christmas Symbolism of Little Jack Horner
description:
Interpreting the nursery rhyme of Little Jack Horner and showing how it contains deep symbolic structures relating to Christmas and the winter solstice. 

My links:  

patreon: https://www.patreon.com/pageauvideos
paypal: https://www.paypal.me/JonathanPageau

The podcast: https://soundcloud.com/jonathan-pagea...
website: http://www.thesymbolicworld.com
facebook: https://www.facebook.com/TheSymbolicW...
twitter: https://twitter.com/pageaujonathan

Song at the beginning is from Akira the Don's Meaning Wave Christmas album.  https://youtu.be/c5K0znZXIo4
